      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and is entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions perfectly, making this a collector-grade example for a discerning buyer.",
