    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. While it still runs, the engine exhibits a noticeable knock, and the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The exterior shows substantial wear, including deep scratches, several dents, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily stained and torn in several places. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, and it is priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
